            <small class="text-muted">
              JB, Houston
            </small>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/img/color hut.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="color hut">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">REVIEWS</h5>
          <p class="card-text">See what other awesome DIY-er's have to say about Pinster!</p>
          <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-primary text-white text-center p-3">
        <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
          <p>This is the best DIY app I've ever used...like...totes!</p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer text-white">
            <small>
              Someone famous in <cite title="DigitalCrafts">DigitalCrafts</cite>
            </small>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/img/origami.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="origami">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Although I'm indoors a lot because of the pandemic, I'm never bored thanks to the awesome diy projects on Pinster!</p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer">
            <small class="text-muted"> Matt D. </small>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
